ĺFor Gwyneth and Arnold, remembered with love
by their children and grandchildren
"Nature's economy shall be the base for our own,
for it is immutable, but ours is secondary" Linnaeus 1740" 
«To Our Beloved Robert Burness
02.07.1950 - 16.05.2010
That laughing eye, whose sunny beam
Our memory would not cherish less,
And oh, that smile! whose joyous gleam
No mortal language can express"Ő
